I have spent several years collecting scientific knowledge from the vast and growing sector of the recognition of lies and it is clear that exposing deception is a modern skill that can easily be learned and can help you very much in today's complex world - especially if your work responsibilities include hiring, organizing interviews, negotiating or leading people.
